{
  "stem": "21786.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And they thought that they killed their daughter for the autopsy was found out that nothing happened.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And so did I, I think, that they were murderers of my sister.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Took me quite a while to come to the realization that life is something quite different.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And something happened to my life.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I was never forbidden anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I was never given any orders.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I was never corrected.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I could do absolutely anything what I wanted.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Luckily, the professors at the gymnasium, without me realizing at that point in time, they somehow were leading me a little bit.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Especially the guy who was our headmaster, who taught Czech, was a remarkable person.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And somehow, when I wanted to take a trip on a canoe or a kayak, somewhere I could do it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I just got the money.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "When I wanted to do this kind of sport or that kind of sport or to go, I mean, to a summer camp or not, or to go to my grandfather whom I loved, my grandmother-- they lived in the country-- I could do that.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Maybe it hurt me later on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "For I was pretty self-dependent, became pretty self-dependent.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hm?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, I went through six years of psychoanalysis.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In spite of that, I have just very, very sporadic memory for the trauma probably.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And especially, the indictment of the parents was so big that it simply blocked the memories.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I say, I know just the little holes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I see Hilda.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We are having a lunch, or a dinner.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she is giving me some kind of food I like.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I don't know whether it was a wiener or whether it was a piece of salami or something like it.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
